    <abstract>
      <t>   This document specifies the Software Inventory Message and Attributes
   for PA-TNC.  It extends the PA-TNC specification [RFC5792] by
   providing specific attributes and message exchanges to allow
   endpoints to report their installed software inventory information to
   a NEA server (as described in [RFC5209]).

	 </t>
